'''Bokone Bophirima''' ke [[:en:Provinces_of_South_Africa|Profense ya Afrika Borwa]]. Moshate wa yona ke [[:en:Mahikeng|Mahikeng]]. Profense e e supelwa bophirima ba [[Gauteng]].

== Histori ==
Bokone Bophirima e ne ya tlhangwa mafelong a  [[:en:Apartheid|Apartheid]] ka ngwaga wa 1994, e akaretsa dikarolo tsa kgale tsa [[:en:Transvaal_Province|Profense ya Transvaal]] le tsa [[:en:Cape_Province|Profense ya Kapa]], le dikarola tsa [[:en:Bantustan|Bantustan]] ya [[Bophuthatswana]]. Go ne ga nna le dintwa le dikgotlhakgotlhano tsa sepolotiki kwa [[:en:Khutsong|Khutsong]], [[:en:Merafong_City_Local_Municipality|Merafong City Local Municipality]] ka ngwaga wa 2006 le wa 2007, morago ga gore di masepala tse di direlang diprofense tse fetang nngwe di tloswe, mme Masepala wa Merafong wa iswa Bokone Bophirima gotlhelele. Masepala wa Merafong o ne wa iswa profenseng ya [[Gauteng]] ka ngwaga wa 2009.

== Molao le golomente ==
Golomente ya profense e akaretsa [[:en:Premier_of_North_West|tonakgolo]], lekgotlha la di mininstara di le lesome, le legislature. Lekgotlha la profense le mininstara ba tlhophwa go nna dingwaga di le tlhano mo setulong, kgotsa go fitlha ditlhopho tse di latelang. Mekgatlho ya sepolotiki e newa ditulo tsa lekgotlha go ya ka palo ya ditlhopho tse mokgatlho o di kereileng mo profenseng ka ditlhopho tsa bosetŝhaba. Lekgotlha ke lona le tlhophang tonakgolo, mme tonakgolo ke ena a (appoint the members of the executive council.)

Tonakgolo ya profense ya Bokone Bophirima, go tloga ka 21 Motsheganong 2014, ke [[:en:Supra_Mahumapelo|Supra Mahumapelo]]<ref>[http://www.nwpg.gov.za North West Provincial Government Official Website]</ref> wa mokgatlho wa [[:en:African_National_Congress|African National Congress]]. O tsenetse Thandi Modise mo setulong sa botonakgolo morago ga ditlhopho tsa 2014.

== Lefatshe ==
[[File:Magaliesberg02.jpg|left|thumb|Hamerkop Kloof magareng ga Rustenburg le Tshwane mo dithabaneng tse di lebileng bokone tsa Magaliesberg]]
Much of the province consists of flat areas of scattered trees and grassland. Dithaba tsa [[:en:Magaliesberg|Magaliesberg]] kwa bokone-botlhaba di botelele jo bo ka nnang 130 km  (go lekana le 80 miles) go tloga [[:en:Pretoria|Tshwane]] goya [[:en:Rustenburg,_North_West|Rustenburg]]. Noka ya [[:en:Vaal_River|Vaal]] e elela mo botareng ya borwa ba profense.

=== Tsa legodimo ===
Di-temperature di tloga go 17° goya go 31&nbsp;°C (62° goya go 88&nbsp;°F) ka selemo, mme go tloga go 3° goya go 21&nbsp;°C (37° goya go 70&nbsp;°F) ka mariga. Pula mo ngwageng ena dimilimitara dile 360 (360&#x20;mm) (go lekana le 14 in), bontsi ba pula e bo na ka dikgwedi tsa selemo, magareng ga Diphalane le Moranang.

=== Dibotara ===
Bokone Bophirima bo arologana di botara le dikgaolo tse di latelang tsa [[Botswana]]:
* Kgatleng – goya bokone-botlhaba<br>
* South-East – bokone-botlhaba
* [[Motsana wa Molapowabojang|Southern]] – bokone
* [[Kgalagadi le dikgaolo tse di mabapi|Kgalagadi]] – bokone-bophirima
Fa gae, e arologana dibotara le diprofense tse di latelang:
* [[Kgaolo ya Limpopo|Limpopo]] – bokone-botlhaba
* [[Gauteng]] – botlhaba
* [[Free State]] – borwa-botlhaba
* [[Northern Cape]] – borwa-bophirima

